:{\"filePath\":\"/Users/gtrrz-victor/.claude/plans/serene-churning-pudding.md\",\"content\":\"# Plan: Fix prompt.txt missing in mid-turn commit checkpoints\\n\\n## Context\\n\\nMid-turn commits (agent commits while still working) produce checkpoints without `prompt.txt` after the first one. All checkpoints in a turn share the same user prompt and should all have it.\\n\\nRoot cause: `extractCheckpointPrompts()` scopes the transcript past where the prompt lives after the first condensation advances `CheckpointTranscriptStart`.\\n\\n## Approach\\n\\nRepurpose `FirstPrompt` on session state to track the **last prompt** instead. Update it on every `InitializeSession` call (each `UserPromptSubmit`). Use it in condensation instead of re-parsing the transcript.\\n\\nAll consumers of `prompt.txt` already truncate (`ExtractFirstPrompt` → 60 chars), and `FirstPrompt` stores 100 runes, so the truncation is fine.\\n\\n## Changes\\n\\n### 1. Rename `FirstPrompt` → `LastPrompt` in session state\\n\\n**`cmd/entire/cli/session/state.go`** (line 142-143):\\n- Rename field from `FirstPrompt` to `LastPrompt`\\n- Keep JSON tag as `\\\"first_prompt\\\"` for backward compat with existing state files\\n- Update comment\\n\\n### 2. Update `LastPrompt` on every turn, not just the first\\n\\n**`cmd/entire/cli/strategy/manual_commit_hooks.go`** — `InitializeSession()` (line 1681-1684):\\n\\nChange from only-backfill-if-empty:\\n```go\\nif state.FirstPrompt == \\\"\\\" && userPrompt != \\\"\\\" {\\n    state.FirstPrompt = truncatePromptForStorage(userPrompt)\\n}\\n```\\nTo always-update:\\n```go\\nif userPrompt != \\\"\\\" {\\n    state.LastPrompt = truncatePromptForStorage(userPrompt)\\n}\\n```\\n\\nAlso update comment on line 1648 (`FirstPrompt` → `LastPrompt`).\\n\\n**`cmd/entire/cli/strategy/manual_commit_session.go`** — `initializeSession()` (line 241):\\n- Rename `FirstPrompt:` → `LastPrompt:` in the initial state struct\\n- Update comment on line 194 (`FirstPrompt` → `LastPrompt`)\\n\\n### 3. Use `LastPrompt` in condensation\\n\\n**`cmd/entire/cli/strategy/manual_commit_condensation.go`**:\\n\\n**`extractSessionData()`** (line 439): Add `turnPrompt string` parameter. At line 465:\\n```go\\nif turnPrompt != \\\"\\\" {\\n    data.Prompts = []string{turnPrompt}\\n} else {\\n    data.Prompts = extractCheckpointPrompts(agentType, data.Transcript, checkpointTranscriptStart)\\n}\\n```\\n\\n**`CondenseSession()` caller** (line 129): Pass `state.LastPrompt` as the new `turnPrompt` argument.\\n\\n**`extractSessionDataFromLiveTranscript()`** (line 504): Already receives `state`, so:\\n```go\\nif state.LastPrompt != \\\"\\\" {\\n    data.Prompts = []string{state.LastPrompt}\\n} else {\\n    data.Prompts = extractCheckpointPrompts(state.AgentType, data.Transcript, state.CheckpointTranscriptStart)\\n}\\n```\\n\\n### 4. Use `LastPrompt` in `finalizeAllTurnCheckpoints`\\n\\n**`cmd/entire/cli/strategy/manual_commit_hooks.go`** (line 2017):\\n```go\\nvar prompts []string\\nif state.LastPrompt != \\\"\\\" {\\n    prompts = []string{state.LastPrompt}\\n} else {\\n    prompts = extractUserPrompts(state.AgentType, string(fullTranscript))\\n}\\n```\\n\\n### 5. Update references\\n\\nRename `FirstPrompt` → `LastPrompt` in:\\n- `cmd/entire/cli/status.go` (line 311-312) — display code\\n- `cmd/entire/cli/strategy/manual_commit_types.go` (lines 17-24) — constant name `maxFirstPromptRunes` → `maxLastPromptRunes`, comments\\n- `cmd/entire/cli/status_test.go` — test fixtures (3 occurrences of `FirstPrompt:`, 1 comment)\\n\\n## Verification\\n\\n1. `mise run fmt && mise run test:ci`\\n2. Integration tests pass (no context.md assertions to worry about on this branch)\\n\",\"numLines\":94,\"startLine\":1,\"totalLines\":94}},\"sourceToolAssistantUUID\":\"b3feba72-8262-4caa-8b62-f2eb9420aa72\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"542c91e3-0fb9-42b4-bf07-13d00a894b9d\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/gtrrz-victor/wks/cli/cli\",\"sessionId\":\"0d411808-78e1-4abb-b5da-