ntent(content)\\n    }\\n}\\n// Filesystem fallback (written at turn start, covers mid-turn commits)\\nif len(data.Prompts) == 0 {\\n    data.Prompts = readPromptsFromFilesystem(ctx, sessionID)\\n}\\n```\\n\\nAlso revert the `turnPrompt` parameter added in the previous attempt.\\n\\n### 3. `extractSessionDataFromLiveTranscript` — read `prompt.txt` from filesystem\\n\\n**`cmd/entire/cli/strategy/manual_commit_condensation.go`** (~line 504):\\n\\nReplace:\\n```go\\ndata.Prompts = extractCheckpointPrompts(state.AgentType, data.Transcript, state.CheckpointTranscriptStart)\\n```\\n\\nWith:\\n```go\\ndata.Prompts = readPromptsFromFilesystem(ctx, state.SessionID)\\n```\\n\\n### 4. `finalizeAllTurnCheckpoints` — read `prompt.txt` from shadow branch, then filesystem\\n\\n**`cmd/entire/cli/strategy/manual_commit_hooks.go`** (~line 2017):\\n\\nReplace:\\n```go\\nprompts := extractUserPrompts(state.AgentType, string(fullTranscript))\\n```\\n\\nWith:\\n```go\\nprompts := readPromptsFromShadowBranch(ctx, repo, state)\\nif len(prompts) == 0 {\\n    prompts = readPromptsFromFilesystem(ctx, state.SessionID)\\n}\\n```\\n\\n### 5. Add helpers\\n\\n**`cmd/entire/cli/strategy/manual_commit_condensation.go`**:\\n\\n- `splitPromptContent(content string) []string` — splits on `\\\"\\\\n\\\\n---\\\\n\\\\n\\\"`\\n- `readPromptsFromFilesystem(ctx, sessionID) []string` — reads `.entire/metadata/<session-id>/prompt.txt`\\n\\n**`cmd/entire/cli/strategy/manual_commit_hooks.go`**:\\n\\n- `readPromptsFromShadowBranch(ctx, repo, state) []string` — reads prompt.txt from shadow branch tree (same pattern as `getLastPrompt()` at line 1891)\\n\\n### 6. Revert previous attempt\\n\\nRevert all `FirstPrompt` → `LastPrompt` renames. No session state changes.\\n\\n## Files Modified\\n\\n- `cmd/entire/cli/lifecycle.go` — write prompt.txt at turn start\\n- `cmd/entire/cli/strategy/manual_commit_condensation.go` — read prompt.txt from shadow branch/filesystem, helpers, revert `turnPrompt`\\n- `cmd/entire/cli/str